LINES.text: MIGHTY ONE, O ANCIENT OF DAYS,
POINT MAN AND PINNING DOWN TWO
ARMED WITH SIX GRENADES AND HIS
THE FIRST GRENADE, IT SAILED TO
TWO OTHER SQUADS WERE ABLE TO
EVEN WHEN THAT AND 60 WAS HIT
WHO WAS SERVING AS  A SECOND
TWO DAYS AFTER HIS AIR AMULETS
CRASHED, HE MADE IT ABOUT FOUR
TWO MORE DAYS FOR ANOTHER SOUTH
HE EVEN CALLED IN ONE STRIKE,
SAVING ONE MORE LIFE ALONG THE
WE DID A MILLER ONE IN WORLD
WAR II ERA WARS RESULTING AT 22
FRIEND OF MINE, ONE OF MY
AWAY AT THE AGE OF 98, THE LAST
HE FIRST DEPLOYED HIS BID TO
WITH RIFLE FIRE AND TWO OTHERS
BEEN ONE TO A FELLOW SHOULDER
THE PILOT MADE A SECOND LANDING
REMAIN BEHIND IS THE ONLY ONE
ALLIED CAMP FOR TWO MORE DAYS
THE CALL OF DUTY WITH THE 11th
